1. *Ona* je povredila nogu skakanjem sa drveta. (She injured her leg by jumping from a tree.)
2. Treba da se pazimo da ne *povredimo* sebe. (We should be careful not to injure ourselves.)
3. Nisam znao da ću *povrediti* tako dete. (I didn't know I would hurt such a child.)
4. *Povredio* je njenu dušu mnogim lažima. (He injured her soul with many lies.)
5. Nije mi bila namera da *povredim* njegovo osećanje. (It was not my intention to hurt his feelings.)